
This is simple shopping cart using Python, Flask, MySQL. This shopping cart is very simple and it does not have checkout option, payment option. 
This is about to display products in an online shopping portal, add item to cart, remove item from cart and remove all items from cart at once or empty cart.

Prerequisites
Python 3.7.4 – 3.9.1, MySQL 8.0.17 – 8.0.22, Flask 1.1.1 – 1.1.2

Installation

1. copy all the folders with files
2. Run the application : project root directory from command line tool and execute the command python main.py or simply main.py, your server will start on default port 5000.
3. Hit URL http://localhost:5000/ in the browser, you will see below output on the browser:

